<p>
	Sweetgrass is also known as Holy Grass, Mary&#39;s Grass, Vanilla Grass, Bluejoint, Buffalo Grass, Manna Grass and Zebrovka. It has a fragrance, almost sweet vanilla-like fragrance it its leaves and is used in Native American culture for prayers, smudging and purifying ceremonies.<br />
	Enjoy the aroma and purifying effects of this sweetgrass incense in your own home.<br />
	Simply light the end of a stick, wait for it to glow then blow out the flame. Place the stick in a safe holder to enjoy the most wonderful fragrances.<br />
	This pack contains approx. 10 sticks. With a burn time each of approx. 45-55 mins.&nbsp;</p>
